fm: vector<int> partitionLabels(string S) {         int start = 0, end = 0, n = S.size();         vector<int> res, pos(26);         for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i)             pos[S[i] - 'a'] = i;         for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i) {             end = max(end, pos[S[i] - 'a']);             if (end == i) {                 res.push_back(end - start + 1);                 start = i + 1;                 end = start;             }         }         return res;     }

fm: int orderOfLargestPlusSign(int N, vector<vector<int>> &mines) {         vector<vector<int>> dp(N, vector<int>(N, N));         for(int i = 0 ; i < mines.size(); ++i)             dp[mines[i][0]][mines[i][1]] = 0;         for (int i = 0; i < N; ++i) {             int l = 0, r = 0, u = 0, d = 0;             for (int j = 0; j < N; ++j) {                 int k = N - j - 1;                 dp[i][j] = min(dp[i][j], l = (dp[i][j] == 0 ? 0 : l + 1));                 dp[i][k] = min(dp[i][k], r = (dp[i][k] == 0 ? 0 : r + 1));                 dp[j][i] = min(dp[j][i], u = (dp[j][i] == 0 ? 0 : u + 1));                 dp[k][i] = min(dp[k][i], d = (dp[k][i] == 0 ? 0 : d + 1));             }         }         int maxSign = 0;         for (int i = 0; i < N; ++i)             for (int j = 0; j < N; ++j)                 maxSign = max(maxSign, dp[i][j]);         return maxSign;     }

fm: int minSwapsCouples(vector<int> &row) {         int res = 0, n = row.size();         vector<int> pos(n);         for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i)             pos[row[i]] = i;         for (int i = 0; i < n; i += 2) {             int p = row[i] % 2 == 0 ? row[i] + 1 : row[i] - 1;             int c = row[i + 1];             if (row[i + 1] != p) {                 swap(row[pos[c]], row[pos[p]]);                 swap(pos[c], pos[p]);                 ++res;             }         }         return res;     }

fm: bool isToeplitzMatrix(vector<vector<int>>& matrix) {         int n = matrix.size();         if(n == 0)             return true;         int m = matrix[0].size();         for(int i = 0; i < n - 1; ++i) {             int temp = matrix[i][0], j = i + 1,k = 1;             while(j < n && k < m) {                 if(matrix[j][k] !=temp)                     return false;                 ++j;                 ++k;             }         }         for(int i = 1; i < m - 1; ++i) {             int temp = matrix[0][i], j = 1,k = i + 1;             while(j < n && k < m) {                 if(matrix[j][k] !=temp)                     return false;                 ++j;                 ++k;             }         }         return true;     }
